code: /**  * Closes this request queue.  *  * @see java.io.Closeable#close()  */ @Override public void close() {     this.closed = true. }

comment: /**  * Checks whether this request queue is closed.  *  * @return True, if the queue is closed, false otherwise.  */
code: /**  * Checks whether this request queue is closed.  *  * @return True, if the queue is closed, false otherwise.  */ public boolean isClosed() {     return this.closed. }
